docs.title: Overview
docs.description: NEAR Protocol offers development paths for WEB2/WEB3 devs to get started with the ecosystem. If you're joining from web2 then Assemblyscript may be a great place to start. Existing web3 devs may find RUST a more natural fit. Whichever path you choose you can find the tools, resources, and support to help you journey through the NEARVerse.

docs.title: What's an NFT?
docs.description: Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs) are digital certificates of ownership for digital assets. These digital certificates are published into an ERC-721 token, and once written, they're secured on the blockchain.
